scenes.description: Outside the house, Kiara is talking to Baby Kobo, who has been turned into a baby by the sky. Kiara tries to teach her how to walk.
Kiara and Kobo go inside to a playroom where many other Hololive members have also been turned into babies. Kiara introduces them one by one.
A mysterious cloud character appears on a monitor, explaining that all the girls on the island have become babies and asks Kiara to babysit.
